Overview:<br />
Cloudant develops cutting-edge data and analytics solutions for the next generation of globally distributed, highly available business applications. &nbsp;</p>
<p>
We&rsquo;re hiring the most talented developers with experience in Erlang/OTP and distributed systems to help us build out our global data platform. We have assembled a top-notch engineering team with deep roots in the open source community. The ideal candidate should have a passion for solving hard problems. By the way, we don&rsquo;t care where you are as long as you&rsquo;re the best. And, guess what, if you&rsquo;re the best and you want to move to sunny Boston? we&rsquo;ll make it happen!</p>
<p>
Primary Objectives:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Working with our core development to build, test, and deploy our globally distributed data service.</li>
</ul>
<p>
Must-Haves:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Demonstrable experience building applications in Erlang</li>
<li>
Experience working with distributed development teams</li>
<li>
Passion for solving hard data problems</li>
<li>
Excellent communications skills, both written and verbal</li>
</ul>
<p>
Nice-to-Haves:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Experience with cloud providers like Amazon EC2, SoftLayer, and RackSpace</li>
<li>
Experience with Apache CouchDB, SaaS, and RESTful services a plus</li>
<li>
History of contributions to Open Source projects</li>
</ul>
<p>
At Cloudant, we are passionate about 2 things: building great software to solve complex data problems and providing an amazing service to our customers. &nbsp;Our team takes pride in seeing our products used by application developers around the world. &nbsp;If this sounds like something you&#39;re interested in, we look forward to hearing from you.</p>
<p>
About Cloudant<br />
Founded in 2008, Cloudant provides the leading global data platform for JSON. Our service allows our customers to collect, replicate and federate JSON. Today, Cloudant&rsquo;s service powers 1,000&rsquo;s of applications that need to scale seamlessly from small to very large datasets, yield realtime insights, and replicate and synchronize data around the world. Cloudant is headquartered in Boston, MA.</p>
